{"tid":1807060,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「是你們教我和平遊行是沒用的」「和勇不分」「核彈都唔割」","createTime":"2020-01-01T15:33:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-02T06:27:09.000Z","uid":205928,"like":28,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"5e350e6ea4c7bfa650e08e6949ff483f9bcebb01","tid":1807060,"uid":205928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T15:33:58.000Z","msg":"係咪過完年之後冇人記得晒？<br />\n記唔記得我哋當初咩原因開始裝修<br />\n記唔記得有一個幾月時間我哋沉迷和平遊行<br />\n記唔記得有個手足係連儂牆俾人打十幾拳而不還手<br />\n係咪依家終於有機會俾你地遊行 就忘記上半年嘅仇恨<br />\n知唔知人哋出嚟做嘢要付上咩代價<br />\n<br />\n定係你想話俾我知香港人冇資格抗爭？"},{"pid":"60839b0da36a2b8859bd9839f2b5d4da88797792","tid":1807060,"uid":205928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T15:37:56.000Z","msg":"有冇人可補補圖<br />\n冇心機揾"},{"pid":"9a04a77688223f7d2b363f73778473828c1a3cfb","tid":1807060,"uid":205928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T15:38:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7d595f6222690c0714fd0dca96972ce9d274ae84","tid":1807060,"uid":205928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T15:38:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4e5fec45551a56f54406712a64ded3bd039c5dcb","tid":1807060,"uid":59297,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T15:40:33.000Z","msg":"港獨思潮<br />\n黃色經濟圈<br />\n組織工會<br />\n<br />\n呢三者將會係我地2020嘅抗爭目標，三者缺一不可<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n首先要思想武裝，認清只有獨立一途，香港已經冇險可守，香港人係一個民族，完全異於所謂中國人，應該建立一個屬於自己嘅國家。<br />\n<br />\n黃色經濟圈同工會就係行動實踐，建立返香港民族嘅經濟實力，從各行各業建立力量，再加強理念宣傳。<br />\n<br />\n去到獨立嘅最後一步，就係等待歷史機會，當中共最脆弱嘅時候，全球反共嘅時候，引用國際法嘅住民自決原則，透過公投宣布獨立<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d5b25e60a3d36963e1c4d75931568f1722c3145","tid":1807060,"uid":205928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T15:40:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1afc45f81e587db949a51a3bca196f1924a38578","tid":1807060,"uid":205928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T15:41:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bbac9d04632670203dc7ea3ba299e9a7b50abd2b","tid":1807060,"uid":272569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T15:43:41.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n[環保撚][1大活動換物][2鳩search]浪費但環保<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1807049\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1807049</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"cb6663b32c4ab62251bab24cba9d90e6a9c10d3c","tid":1807060,"uid":256952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T21:49:07.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"00d41592a4a02682c3ffd00f511fc5571148a53e","tid":1807060,"uid":205928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cb6663b32c4ab62251bab24cba9d90e6a9c10d3c","tid":1807060,"uid":256952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T21:49:07.000Z","msg":"支持"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T21:49:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />冇人覆我"},{"pid":"6f48949ef56de87b117aa3e0fe2b18f7afee7a55","tid":1807060,"uid":256952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"00d41592a4a02682c3ffd00f511fc5571148a53e","tid":1807060,"uid":205928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cb6663b32c4ab62251bab24cba9d90e6a9c10d3c","tid":1807060,"uid":256952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T21:49:07.000Z","msg":"支持"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T21:49:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />冇人覆我"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T21:54:20.000Z","msg":"我錫哂你<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5add010e1c65e3dc4d30648e7d236bb91746f812","tid":1807060,"uid":205928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"